forall start, middle, last Z, c R:
    start <= middle <= middle + 1<= last
    =>:
        sum(i, start, last + 1, i) = sum(i, start, last, i) + (last + 1)
        sum(i, start, middle, i) + sum(i, middle + 1, last, i) = sum(i, start, last, i)
        sum(i, start, last, i + i) = sum(i, start, last, i) + sum(i, start, last, i)
        sum(i, start, start, i) = start